# poissonDistributionPdf

- _poissonDistributionPdf(lambda, x)_

Answer the probability density function for the Poisson distribution.

Plot over the positive integers:

~~~
let lambda = 35;
0:60.functionPlot { :x |
	poissonDistributionPdf(lambda, x)
}
~~~

